race.comment: MILITARIZE (7) ready to peak fifth-up and worth noting Joao Moreira rode him to his last victory in the 2023 Golden Rose. Took good ground off Lindermann from back in the pack when a slashing second in the G3 Craven Plt over 1800m at Randwick. Down in weight and this looks a target race. Value play. VIVY AIR (13) went back from the wide draw and produced one of the runs of the day when a tough second over 1600m in the LR Big Dance at Randwick on Tuesday. Will run the trip and take hand in the finish. TRANSATLANTIC (1) gone to a new level this prep but faces a few hurdles out to the 1800m today from the wide gate. Berry retains the ride and looks under the odds at $2.70. RISE AT DAWN (8) huge effort when third in the G2 Crystal Mile at Moonee Valley over the mile. Can take control early and prove hard to catch from the inside gate. BULLET POINT (3) resumes for the Haggas' yard with the four wins over the mile in the UK. Stable must always be respected when they bring one here.
